    <div class="prose">
        <h2>What we collect</h2>
        <p>While @Brand.Name is a read-only preview, we collect very little. We use a session cookie to keep
            the site working and to understand, in aggregate, how the listings are browsed. We don't ask you
            to create an account to look around.</p>

        <h2>Contacting a venue</h2>
        <p>When you contact a venue, your message goes to that venue by email — you're emailing them directly,
            not through a @Brand.Name inbox. Anything you put in that message is shared with the venue, not with us.</p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>We set one essential, first-party session cookie. We don't use third-party advertising or
            cross-site tracking cookies.</p>

        <h2>What we don't do</h2>
        <p>We don't sell your data, and we don't share it with advertisers.</p>

        <h2>Your choices &amp; contact</h2>
        <p>You can browse without signing in or providing personal details. For any privacy question, or to
            ask us to remove information, get in touch via the <a href="~/about">about page</a>.</p>

        <p class="prose-note">This is a preview policy and will be replaced with a full, dated privacy policy
            before launch.</p>
